{"tha-ap323:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap323:0.2":"Umapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap323:0.3":"1 Umapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap323:1.1":"“Samahitam samapannam, ","tha-ap323:1.2":"siddhatthamaparajitam; ","tha-ap323:1.3":"Samadhina upavittham, ","tha-ap323:1.4":"addasaham naruttamam. ","tha-ap323:2.1":"Umapuppham gahetvana, ","tha-ap323:2.2":"buddhassa abhiropayim; ","tha-ap323:2.3":"Sabbapuppha ekasisa, ","tha-ap323:2.4":"uddhamvanta adhomukha. ","tha-ap323:3.1":"Sucitta viya titthante, ","tha-ap323:3.2":"akase pupphasanthara; ","tha-ap323:3.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap323:3.4":"tusitam upapajjaham. ","tha-ap323:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap323:4.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap323:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap323:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap323:5.1":"Pancapannasito kappe, ","tha-ap323:5.2":"eko asim mahipati; ","tha-ap323:5.3":"Samantachadano nama, ","tha-ap323:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap323:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap323:6.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap323:6.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap323:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap323:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma umapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap323:8.1":"Umapupphiyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}